## ğŸš€ Installation

### Windows
```powershell
# Download ZIP from GitHub, extract to Desktop, then:
cd ~\Desktop\BugPredict-AI-main

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Verify installation
python -c "from src.collectors import CSVImporter; print('âœ“ Installation successful!')"
```

### Linux/Mac
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/BugPredict-AI.git
cd BugPredict-AI

# Create virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Verify installation
python -c "from src.collectors import CSVImporter; print('âœ“ Installation successful!')"
```

