## ğŸ¯ Supported Vulnerability Types

| # | Vulnerability Type | Severity Range | Nuclei Template |
|---|-------------------|----------------|-----------------|
| 1 | SQL Injection | High - Critical | âœ… |
| 2 | XSS (Cross-Site Scripting) | Medium - High | âœ… |
| 3 | SSRF (Server-Side Request Forgery) | High - Critical | âœ… |
| 4 | IDOR (Insecure Direct Object Reference) | Medium - High | âœ… |
| 5 | CSRF (Cross-Site Request Forgery) | Medium - High | âœ… |
| 6 | Authentication Bypass | Critical | âœ… |
| 7 | RCE (Remote Code Execution) | Critical | âœ… |
| 8 | XXE (XML External Entity) | High - Critical | âœ… |
| 9 | Path Traversal | Medium - High | âœ… |
| 10 | Information Disclosure | Low - Medium | âœ… |

**Each template includes:**
- Multiple attack vectors
- Pattern matchers
- Severity ratings
- CWE mappings

